    "name": "魔力熔炉大亨",
    "steam_appid": 3073070,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/93d665827ce9d5f6361db04b9cfd4fb0.avif?t=1768815780\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >锻造传奇，塑造王国！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在魔法锻造厂，每一锤都在塑造历史。管理你的星界锻造工坊，打造魔法武器，并决定战乱王国的命运。是助长战争，还是用你的技艺铸造和平？掌控经济，完成贵族与君主的订单，让你的名字载入史册，成为传奇铁匠！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/8ce75593f653b61cba546ba5cd14d2ea.poster.avif?t=1768815780\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/8ce75593f653b61cba546ba5cd14d2ea.webm?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/8ce75593f653b61cba546ba5cd14d2ea.mp4?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精通锻造技艺</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择最优的武器图纸，精细调整每个细节，并施加强大的魔法，打造无与伦比的武器品质。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在风格与耐久之间找到完美平衡，打造独一无二的传奇武器。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升生产效率，优化锻造流程，打造适合王者的巅峰之作。</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >扩展并升级你的工坊</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >购买新技术，加快生产速度，让你的武器更加完美。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的锻造工坊，解锁先进的制造技术，提高生产能力。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >投资研究，发现全新武器设计与稀有资源，提升你的锻造水平。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/e6ea2cf48d4ca141c2b98119dac90146.poster.avif?t=1768815780\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/e6ea2cf48d4ca141c2b98119dac90146.webm?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/e6ea2cf48d4ca141c2b98119dac90146.mp4?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控经济与贸易</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在一个动态市场中买卖材料，该市场受战争、联盟与资源短缺影响。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >囤积原材料，预测价格波动与王国冲突，确保最大收益。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >合理管理资源——一次错误投资或材料短缺都可能导致严重后果！</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >影响战争与政治</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完成敌对派系的订单，看着你的武器如何改变权力平衡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >积累影响力点数，解锁更优订单、政治特权和工坊独家加成。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在关键区域建立贸易前哨，扩大你的影响力，并获取重要情报。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/28656af8699e0bee0a56617a064ae94a.poster.avif?t=1768815780\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/28656af8699e0bee0a56617a064ae94a.webm?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/28656af8699e0bee0a56617a064ae94a.mp4?t=1768815780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的选择决定世界的变化</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的经济决策能让王国繁荣……或走向衰亡。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >战争、联盟和经济动态变化，为每次游戏带来新的挑战。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你锻造的每一把武器都会留下历史的印记。你是和平的缔造者，还是战争的商人？</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成为王国最伟大的铁匠！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >魔法锻造厂融合了直观的玩法与深度管理机制，构建了一个生动而变化多端的世界。扩展你的锻造工坊，掌控市场，见证你的作品如何影响王国的命运！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>将游戏加入愿望单，在火焰与钢铁中锻造属于你的传奇！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3073070/extras/93d665827ce9d5f6361db04b9cfd4fb0.avif?t=1768815780\" width=616 height=150 /></span></p>",
